<p>The getDay() function returns the weekday as a number:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
var d = new Date();
var week = ["Sunday", "Monday", "Tuesday", "Wednesday", "Thursday", "Friday", "Saturday"]
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = week[d.getDay()];
</script>

</body>
